Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:37.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介之父纯情啊！\N妻子的身影在回忆中！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈离家之后十数年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么恶心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有点儿怀念你妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲我代母之名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一针一线投以感情所织的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然拒绝父亲我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要穿这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓图案 有花形的内…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓图案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尾熊图案 还有熊猫图案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何呢 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲怎么会不了解你的喜好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海蓝色的女生制服模样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这变态老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我憧憬的女生制服给…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也算男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不是在扫保健室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是保健室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别打扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦 来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗 卑鄙的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 谁卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够…了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一直过这种打架的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天脸会扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打架会打输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸给毁了还比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子应该更加珍惜脸才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样下去嫁不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就一直想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸围是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰围是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀围是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就一直想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么慎重怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 有谈过恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人和女人因爱而在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱早在小学一年级已经经历过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是班级老师 年轻 清爽 而且温柔的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是个爱哭的老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且短裙很适合他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没多久就嫁人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我可是哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此有个问题想问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿短裙且嫁人的是男人还是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开我玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人怎么可能穿裙子嫁人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你的初恋者是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是个小小的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学三年级坐在隔壁的久美子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学六年级时同班的美树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中一的贵子也是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绘 加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在喜欢的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不行 这样不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 喜欢也不是那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是变态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你还没有恋爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能真正爱上男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你会变得像女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能变得像女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 显然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我来帮你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这由我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别粘人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理想中的男人是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像海洋般的奔放 强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我打架还强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 你喜欢父亲我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前从来就不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全符合龙之介的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 我为何要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害什么羞呀 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但龙之介你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人相互爱慕是不得了之事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们还是父子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你乱七八糟的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介才对男人毫无兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了可爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要饮泣结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要结婚 你就会死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 定情之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 定情之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一块橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰我要的是橡皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰要的是橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是结婚的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期日可惜是“佛灭”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来就是大安了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小兰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为龙之介后母 小兰不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是称为妈妈或母亲比较恰当嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我 快点 交出来 橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是往常用的橡皮是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你困扰了 所以不用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 小兰好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新母亲的家庭经济观念很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样父亲我也能安心投入工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果真想结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有其他方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？你吃你父亲的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲我不能和儿子结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请了解龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这样的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈会哭泣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时候也是这样一付寂寞的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不让我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友的交往也很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是清爽的东西可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特制的梅子豆沙烤饼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很清爽的 多吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我以为合你的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上那天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了鳟鱼还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆沙的麻薯89个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在那幻影之梅子豆沙烤饼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭也不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人真辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想过再婚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未想过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是时候了 从未想过再娶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是校长为何提及此事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为受了樱花老师之托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是相亲照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事请恕我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸那小子勉强什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子 我以为这念头早丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刨木屑的清洁剂汤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷子的炸肉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠菜及强力胶的小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芦笋的抹布卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想结婚 别太在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想也不大可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没必要哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是开个玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸今天很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不像我的作风对再婚动心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了你母亲的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直吃那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁都会肚子疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介再靠近点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好好看看你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回个应嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真听人家说话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有认真说话之心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我想拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否穿上你母亲的衣服给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花开花的区域现在到哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要我穿妈妈的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请你也了解父亲我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样也无法率真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再说 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念 一切都犹如从前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何穿妈妈的衣服要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你母亲第一次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在此打工之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲也是为学费在打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一年春天 我与你母亲都年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋 海滨店特制的冰淇淋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在儿童乐园要关门之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人烟罕至的夜樱树下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎感到那是我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个似曾相识般相遇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说马上坠入情网
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测谎机并没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不像往常 说了真话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 你父亲说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为女人的服装多少有点费事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿的事就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙 我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮忙穿戴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介这里有母亲的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两人第一次相会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的回忆之物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少有点旧了也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的体形很像你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想会很合身的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然有会让我吃惊的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次如此都让我想起你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是像母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为怕想起逃走的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才以男孩的方式养育龙之介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真自私
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！决定了就换装
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！在你父亲未改变心意前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换衣服要在哪儿换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托以前的熟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室借你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别在这里乱跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前面的内衣开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是束腰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介转过身来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开双手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸要被压破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 藤波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我不能如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必须换衣服 帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我初次见面时穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不是裙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有长靴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮带及手套
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是奇怪的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我真的不能原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把你揍死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子我好想你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法相信 和真砂子一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那样的装扮是很多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然相信你 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认你蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我发誓没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁蠢 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在儿童乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打特摄英雄表演怪兽之工
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你母亲是为赚学费打工演英雄的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽？英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是螺之煮熟怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测测看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个相似遭遇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠入情网是不用多言的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么恋爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不相信此事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的母亲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天请来了电视特摄的超级英雄来到此地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么顺序介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么英雄动作秀开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多的真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子 我不要你恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰想要买羊羹的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪因为感冒需要被炉猫的胡须
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁天不知为何躺下了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我经常是贫穷的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天的浪漫！？因阿雪感冒而冻僵了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:10.24,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:13.41,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.98,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.88,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:23.44,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:50.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.35,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:59.40,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:03.14,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:06.56,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:12.29,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.51,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:17.72,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:19.85,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:25.18,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:30.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:36.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.34,0:24:41.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.12,0:24:49.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:53.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.98,0:24:56.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:01.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.67,0:25:05.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.64,0:25:09.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.56,0:25:12.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:16.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:20.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.02,0:25:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.19,0:25:27.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.83,0:25:31.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

